narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: It's worth it to do the intensive. It's great to get to know the faculty as well as the other people in the major. It's also so fulfilling to complete a year-long project.
A workshop for your senior essay where you get to know your fellow intensive majors and get great feedback on your draft work.
Prof. Smith is great. This was a captivating, engaging experience
If you're doing the intensive major you don't have a choice, but the class is actually pretty fun. Bonding with the other majors, food, and you do get good feedback about your project.
yes. you have to if you're a soc major, but it's fun and helpful.
